<pre><code class="language-python">w = 40 * size
pygame.draw.rect(screen, body_color, (x, HEIGHT - 120, w, 50))
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Hint:</strong> <code>40 * 1.2</code> is a decimal. Pygame sizes must be whole numbers.</p>
<p><strong>Write the fixed code:</strong></p>
